# EXAMPLE CONFIGURATIONS
# ============================================================================

# --- Example 1: Simple Single Monitor ---
# default {
#   path ~/Pictures/my-wallpaper.png
#   mode fill
# }

# --- Example 2: Laptop + External Monitor ---
